{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"人民的心就是一切——欢呼五届人大二次会议开幕","authors":["辛笛"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":6,"day":27}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的心就是一切"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——欢呼五届人大二次会议开幕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛笛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，新中国的土地上谁能欢乐而自由？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是人民，只有人民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁获得人民的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁就有了一切！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，党向人民交了心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也把燃烧的希望交给人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了明天而调整，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是今天九亿人民靠党这样近！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有上有下，下是为了上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有进有退，退是为了进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"短线中有长，长线中有短，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作深入细致，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尺寸才能这样分明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颟顸的作风要整顿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贪污盗窃要判刑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺张浪费不允许，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人来动手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关起有形和无形的“后门”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士们的亲属收拾起眼泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牢记对“四人帮”的仇恨；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亿万颗炽热的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳跃、交织在一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远跟着党前进！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"发言"}]}]}